					Text = "Hey, did you see? My brother, he's come back! He's here! Somewhere, I think! Good old Thanatos. He's so busy all the time, he... never talks to me! Kind of like your dad with {#DialogueItalicFormat}you{#PreviousFormat}, I guess!" },
