					PreLineThreadedFunctionName = "PlayEmoteAnimFromSource", PreLineThreadedFunctionArgs = { Emote = "PortraitEmoteSparkly", WaitTime = 3.65 },
					Text = "Well you know what this means, don't you? We're {#DialogueItalicFormat}official co-workers now{#PreviousFormat}!! Isn't that so exciting? We can share our latest learnings, compare notes about the challenges we're up against, run into one another in the hall..." },
